ZH: 医生告诉我每天吃一次药，剂量是一粒。
EN: The doctor told me to take one pill a day as a dosage.

ZH: 这种药要按照剂量进行使用，不能随便增加或减少。
EN: This medicine should be used according to the dosage and cannot be increased or decreased casually.

ZH: 请注意，这种药的剂量是根据体重来计算的。
EN: Please note that the dosage of this medicine is calculated based on body weight.

ZH: 根据医生的建议，我需要每天注射一定剂量的胰岛素。
EN: According to the doctor's suggestion, I need to inject a certain dosage of insulin every day.

ZH: 这种药的剂量需要逐渐增加，以达到理想的效果。
EN: The dosage of this medicine needs to be gradually increased in order to achieve the desired effect.

ZH: 切勿超过医生规定的剂量，以免产生副作用。
EN: Do not exceed the prescribed dosage by the doctor to avoid side effects.

ZH: 这种药的剂量太大了，我不敢服用。
EN: The dosage of this medicine is too high, I dare not take it.

ZH: 每次服用这种药的剂量应该是一勺。
EN: The dosage of this medicine should be one spoonful each time.

ZH: 病人的剂量已经用完了，需要及时补充。
EN: The patient's dosage has run out and needs to be replenished in time.

ZH: 按照剂量，这瓶药可以供应一个月。
EN: According to the dosage, this bottle of medicine can last for one month.

ZH: 请确保准确使用药物剂量，以免影响疗效。
EN: Please ensure accurate use of the medication dosage to avoid affecting the efficacy.

ZH: 需要提醒患者按时按量服用药物剂量。
EN: Patients need to be reminded to take medication dosage on time and in the correct amount.

ZH: 医生建议我每天按时服用抗生素，并坚持完整的剂量。
EN: The doctor advised me to take antibiotics on time every day and to complete the full dosage.

ZH: 请勿将剂量过量，否则会对健康造成危害。
EN: Do not overdose on the dosage, as it can be harmful to health.

ZH: 您需要按照剂量慢慢减少药物的使用，而不是突然停止。
EN: You need to gradually reduce the usage of the medication according to the dosage, instead of stopping suddenly.

ZH: 这种药需要空腹服用，并按照医生建议的剂量来服用。
EN: This medicine should be taken on an empty stomach and in the dosage recommended by the doctor.

ZH: 您需要定时测量与剂量有关的指标，以确保疗效。
EN: You need to regularly measure indicators related to the dosage to ensure efficacy.

ZH: 在给宠物喂药时，请准确掌握剂量，避免过量。
EN: When giving medication to pets, please accurately control the dosage to avoid overdose.

ZH: 这种药的剂量要求每天分次服用，不能一次性吃完。
EN: The dosage of this medicine requires it to be taken in divided doses throughout the day, not all at once.

ZH: 老年人的剂量可能需要根据身体情况作出调整。
EN: The dosage for elderly people may need to be adjusted based on their physical condition.
